OL,3,CBrothers left in limbo after asylum
OL,4,Cclaim freeze
OL,6,FBrothers Bahaa and Omar Bayan live and
OL,7,Fstudy in Omagh.
OL,9,FThe 19 and 23 year old's fled the war
OL,10,Fin Syria with their family in 2016,
OL,11,Fand were invited to the UK as part of
OL,12,Fthe resettlement scheme.
OL,14,FThe media students have now been told
OL,15,Fby the Home Office their application
OL,16,Fto stay here permanently, known as
OL,17,FIndefinite Leave to Remain, has been
OL,18,Fpaused.
