OL,6,FOmar along with his brother are about
OL,7,Fto graduate from the South West
OL,8,FCollege in Omagh.
OL,10,FOmar said: "I'm still unable to work
OL,11,Fand I'm still unable to like have
OL,12,Fhousing and and just to live like like
OL,13,Fnormally I cannot since I don't take
OL,14,Fbenefits and I don't I cannot rely on
OL,15,Fmy child. It's kind of a limbo that
OL,16,FI'm living in".
OL,18,F"They decided a time frame for that
OL,19,Fpause or that decision, and it was
OL,20,Fvery stressful for me". he added
