OL,6,FThe letter from the Home Office says
OL,7,Fthey have temporarily paused all
OL,8,Fdecisions on claims from Syrian
OL,9,Fnationals across the asylum system as
OL,10,Fthey assess the current situation in
OL,11,Fthe country.
OL,13,F"Thank you for your application for
OL,14,FSettlement.
OL,16,F"Although we would normally decide
OL,17,Fyour application within six months
OL,18,Ffrom the date it was submitted,
OL,19,Funfortunately this is not going to be
OL,20,Fpossible in your case.
