OL,6,F"The Home Office has temporarily
OL,7,Fpaused all decisions on claims from
OL,8,FSyrian nationals, across the asylum
OL,9,Fsystem, whilst we assess the current
OL,10,Fsituation.
OL,12,F"We keep all country guidance relating
OL,13,Fto asylum claims under constant review
OL,14,Fso we can respond to emerging issues.
OL,16,F"The Home Office who has
OL,17,Fresponsibility for asylum decisions
OL,18,Fhas acted swiftly to make the position
OL,19,Fon a pause clear in a fast-moving
OL,20,Fsituation".
