OL,6,FWithout indefinite leave to remain.
OL,7,FThe boys can't apply for citizenship
OL,8,Fand get a passport and can't leave the
OL,9,FUK.
OL,11,F"My sister is in Turkey, and they and
OL,12,Fher daughter died. I'm unable to be
OL,13,Fthere to support her. And general
OL,14,Fmentally, I'm unable there to be there
OL,15,Fto support her physically because she
OL,16,Fisn't Turkish. She is also unable to
OL,17,Fgo back to Syria", Bahaa told UTV.
OL,19,FIt's understood most of all the
OL,20,FSyrians had arrived through the SVR
OL,21,Fscheme have now obtained settlement.
