OL,6,FLiz Griffith from the Law Society
OL,7,Fsaid: "The law centre is currently
OL,8,Fhelping about more than 30 people who
OL,9,Fare in this position.
OL,11,F"They are long time residents, lawful
OL,12,Fresidents and now their applications
OL,13,Fhave been paused, leaving them in a
OL,14,Fkind of legal limbo situation.
OL,16,F"Although they have a type of status,
OL,17,Fthey haven't been given any
OL,18,Fdocumentation, so they cannot prove it.
